{"ja299:0.1":"Jataka ","ja299:0.2":"Tikanipata ","ja299:0.3":"Kumbhavagga ","ja299:0.4":"9. Komaraputtajataka ","ja299:1.1":"“Pure tuvam silavatam sakase, ","ja299:1.2":"Okkantikam kilasi assamamhi; ","ja299:1.3":"Karohare makkatiyani makkata, ","ja299:1.4":"Na tam mayam silavatam ramama”. ","ja299:2.1":"“Suta hi mayham parama visuddhi, ","ja299:2.2":"Komaraputtassa bahussutassa; ","ja299:2.3":"Ma dani mam manni tuvam yatha pure, ","ja299:2.4":"Jhananuyutto viharami avuso”. ","ja299:3.1":"“Sacepi selasmi vapeyya bijam, ","ja299:3.2":"Devo ca vasse na hi tam virulhe; ","ja299:3.3":"Suta hi te sa parama visuddhi, ","ja299:3.4":"Ara tuvam makkata jhanabhumiya”ti. ","ja299:4.1":"Komaraputtajatakam navamam. "}